int16_t  frameTotalChirps,
uint16_t *  validChirpTxEnBits,
bool  bpmEnabled 
)
static

Description
Helper function that parses chirp Tx antenna configuration and extracts parameters needed for AoA configuration depending on the AoA DPU needs

Parameters
[in,out]outParamsPointer to parameters generated after parsing configuration
[in,out]pFoundValidProfileflag to indicate if this is valid profile; if not, advance to the next one
[in]frameTotalChirpsTotal chirps in the frame (used for looping through validChirpTxEnBits)
[in]validChirpTxEnBitsArray of chirp's txEn bits. Dimension is provided by frameTotalChirps
[in]bpmEnabledBPM flag, 0 -disabled, 1-enabled
Return values
Success- 0 Fail <0, one of error codes RF Parser Error Codes
